  {
    "date": "2026-04-16 14:14",
    "weekly_narrative": "本週全球市場被強韌的通膨數據與地緣政治僵局籠罩。美國 3 月 PPI 創下三年新高，配合伊朗談判破裂導致原油價格攀升至 91.43 美元，直接封鎖了聯準會本月降息的可能性。US10Y 殖利率穩定於 4.282% 高位，反映出市場對「更高、更久」利率環境的定價。儘管殖利率居高不下，標普500 指數仍試圖守住 7022.95 點位，顯示 AI 驅動的長期成長動能與高借貸成本間的角力。最具指標性的是黃金價格衝上 4846.4 美元，這表明避險資金正以前所未有的速度從信用貨幣轉向實體資產，防範即將到來的購買力侵蝕。",
    "next_week_forecast_html": "<details class='analysis-container'><summary>📢 下週預測：粘性通膨下的資產大洗牌</summary><div class='analysis-content'><strong>⛓️ 市場邏輯傳導：</strong><p>地緣政治緊張帶動能源價格攀升 ➔ 影響<strong>通膨預期與美債殖利率同步走高</strong> ➔ 最終定價<strong>美元在避險與通膨間的平衡走勢</strong>。</p><hr><strong>📉 資產動態預測：</strong><ul><li><strong>亞洲貨幣 (TWD/JPY/KRW)：</strong>由於美元指數受阻於 98 關口，亞幣短期貶值壓力稍緩，但高油價造成的輸入型通膨將迫使亞太央行維持高利率。</li><li><strong>避險成本與鋼鐵業：</strong>黃金極端報價反映市場對地緣政治的極度恐懼，鋼鐵與能源密集產業將因生產端通膨持續承壓，毛利率面臨下修風險。</li></ul></div></details>",
    "focus_html": "\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">01</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>通膨二次探頭：PPI 與原油雙擊</h4>\n                <p>3 月批發通膨數據超預期攀升，主要驅動因子為原油價格站穩 91.43 美元及 AI 帶來的巨大電力能源需求。市場擔憂能源成本將持續向終端傳導，引發通膨螺旋。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">02</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>聯準會路徑：從降息期待轉向抗通膨防禦</h4>\n                <p>隨著伊朗外交協商陷入停滯，市場已完全排除本月降息的機率。4.282% 的美債殖利率反映出債券市場已進入通膨防禦模式，壓抑了企業的擴張意願。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
    "fx_rates_linkage": "美元指數目前在 98.028 附近呈現「高位滯漲」態勢。雖然美債 4.282% 的利差優勢依然存在，但因 ECB 官員釋放 4 月可能動息的信號，且非美央行普遍轉向抗通膨鷹派，抵消了美元的部分漲勢。與此同時，比特幣報 75054.0 美元與黃金同步上漲，顯示投資者在強勢美元與高通膨環境下，正尋求與傳統法幣體系脫鉤的替代資產，這種避險分流削弱了美元指數的突破動能。",
    "tbody_html": "\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🔥 通膨預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">CPI/PPI Outlook</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">持續擴張 <span class=\"status_detail\">PPI 創三年新高，原油 91.43 美元推升生產端成本。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">上升螺旋</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">地緣政治緊張、AI 能源需求、供應鏈成本回升。</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">📉 利率預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">Fed Funds / US10Y</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">高位橫盤 <span class=\"status_detail\">US10Y 報 4.282%，市場已排除本月降息可能性。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">偏鷹盤整</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">伊朗談判破裂、粘性通膨數據、就業市場強韌。</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🦅 美元指數</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">DXY Strength</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-down\">擴張受阻 <span class=\"status_detail\">DXY 報 98.028，利差優勢被非美央行鷹派態度稀釋。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-down \">橫盤偏弱</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">避險資產分流至黃金與比特幣、非美央行轉鷹。</td>\n                </tr>",
    "risk_html": "\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ 滯脹風險 (Stagflation)</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">若 PPI 增速持續傳導至 CPI，而高利率開始壓抑就業市場（如 AI 引發的結構性失業），全球可能進入成長停滯但物價攀升的惡劣環境。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ 地緣政治升級</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">中東局勢若進一步惡化，原油可能突破 100 美元大關，屆時將引發更劇烈的資產重新定價。</p>\n        </div>",
    "news_html": "\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Is AI going to lead to 20% unemployment - or just make your employees superhuman? - Insurance Business</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiogFBVV95cUxPcHZhcGFmRE1aMVVGU0hZUUtsUDB3WHFPMmI3VUdITE01cEdTUE1vd1F4REFPZjZlWEdCOFQtcGNJLXlhQkFyR2RkOUxSWGxtVUVKU2pfVnFzeWlEc0lLV3NoblM5dThFc0h6TEtpcGRQWTVjck1GYjUzdWN3LTF5bG1KRVozTGFOSmNnczNnVlFia0FSczNzcFY2WWZVMDNNVmc?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 ECB’s Muller: Rate move at April meeting still possible but not guaranteed - Crypto Briefing</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMisgFBVV95cUxQaGs5U1FBaVdzb2NKQ1M2ZXVrMUNYUlNIRTF0VXRmS1RRUlRYZ1lPNFBMUEVOWmhnM0h5UmZSOEZLYW9YcjhhTV9Wb2t3amlGdmV6dThuM1hRbFVZVzN6d1ZrWU9DNkJfSVd1ek9HcGoxQ2x5eHk0dE1vZDJoZUFZbDRiNU1fUHh2UnhoSkh6YVBJNS1JYTJnSnp3VTNVS1FTLU03R1ZQOG1KTUJfR2d2aWlR?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Inflation or recession? The tug of war in bond markets - The Economist</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Nine in ten older US workers say inflation is reshaping their retirement plans - InvestmentNews</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 10-year Treasury yield hovers near 4.3% after oil price gain, sticky inflation data - CNBC</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMikwFBVV95cUxQUDNHRXBWVHlJdjZ4MmxjNWFIX1JPTjhIVm1JbmFRdmFaQVc2WGUxT3AxR2UzeXBlTUw3SGp1ZHRJT2s2Rm5yVHo3NlpVdUJacWdsb3pWWTVzNlVKVkJKUXJNUG5KYmxWeGlBUkYxdFJOQldtZm9VMXFoTnZaU3BvZEhmRmFfaHNYMUd1cmc3YjJOM00?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Wholesale inflation rose in March to three year-high - KSL News</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMihgFBVV95cUxNRVVXQmhEMW51SjNTVDdNeUdTWDJQVVpjZGozRHgyRFlFSEhGVFAydzZyQ3Bya3cxUFN5Y01MUUJmeEdhYkRUYUp1UXRqbWFiS1dNMjEyaEJZNlFOTVk0anh4ZkpMbGhncGxKa2RsNl9BZG9zcFR5SHRBcENOZWY3Y3ZESVBZUQ?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Investors are writing off any move from the Fed this month. Collapsing talks in Iran have sealed the deal - Fortune</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiZkFVX3lxTE1PcmdpYzdnSTBWckxQM0FmcmxiNUYzWW9Va2hlQ3B0d0R2THp1ZXpMMU9yeTlCak5OY3V6aHhycUE4NVlHZEVqUDB6eGIzcXJjNC1La1VwT3YzVjFmODVxRXJ3V05NZw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Inflation, deflation, and the “Goldilocks scenario” - Britannica</a>\n                </li>"
